OL,3,CUK to conduct Middle East
OL,4,Csurveillance flights to help find
OL,5,CHamas hostages
OL,7,FThe UK will conduct unarmed
OL,8,Fsurveillance flights over the Middle
OL,9,FEast to search for potential hostage
OL,10,Flocations being used by Hamas, the
OL,11,FMinistry of Defence (MoD) confirmed
OL,12,Fon Saturday.
OL,14,FThe flights will be purely for
OL,15,Fsurveillance purposes, the department
OL,16,Fsaid, and will be unarmed. Only
OL,17,Finformation that could be useful in
OL,18,Frescuing hostages will be passed on
OL,19,Fto the relevant authorities.
